                h3.h5.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-camera-video.me-2
                  | Kendrick Lamar Super Bowl LIX Halftime Show: A Masterpiece of Metaphors
              .card-body
                p.card-text.mb-3
                  | Experience the full performance and its layered meanings through this comprehensive video analysis that breaks down the symbolic elements and social commentary.
