                    i.bi.bi-shield-check.me-2
                    | Official NFL Recording                  p.mb-0.text-muted.small
                    | Click the link above, then return to our detailed analysis

            .alert.alert-warning.border-0.shadow-sm.mb-4
              .d-flex.align-items-start
