                        p.card-text.small Individuals become engrossed in societal 'games,' losing sight of reality.

                p.mb-0
                  | The PlayStation, a device synonymous with control and immersion, symbolized how individuals can become engrossed in societal 'games,' losing sight of reality and autonomy.

            a(href='#table-of-contents' class='d-block mb-4 text-decoration-none')
              i.bi.bi-arrow-up-circle.me-1
              | Back to Top

          // Squid Game Symbolism Section
          section#squid-game-symbolism.mb-5
            h2.h3.text-primary.mb-4
              i.bi.bi-square.me-2
              | 'Squid Game' Card Symbolism

            .card.shadow-sm.border-0
              .card-header.bg-danger.text-white
